{"tid":816444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶] [澳門良心] 停電期間狼胎加價 150元兩支水100元一盒叉燒飯","createTime":"2018-09-12T18:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T00:37:52.000Z","uid":3189,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc0ba075642afc57b987b4b701a051921327bb1","tid":816444,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/020009_d9591b21d03a24adfc01215f9d1b8d21.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F020009_d9591b21d03a24adfc01215f9d1b8d21.png&h=ddb4c2e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/020012_621ea2d112c78ad90b3f278bd1fe22d1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F020012_621ea2d112c78ad90b3f278bd1fe22d1.png&h=2b186b4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/13/020016_e76abcac7d55a4ce2efc16962746864e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F13%2F020016_e76abcac7d55a4ce2efc16962746864e.png&h=6a4edea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「天鴿」吹襲澳門期間造成嚴重破壞，不少地區更停電斷水。有當地藥房和餐廳座地起價，一支在香港賣10元有找的700毫升蒸餾水，昨日在澳門藥房竟賣兩支合共150元，有燒味店一盒叉燒飯賣100元。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛批評商店「發災難財」，「飯都算，兩支水真係離X曬譜」、「75蚊一支水，仲貴過酒店」。"},{"pid":"c3c3a8cb9f6791b0dbbafe5dfe1418fec6472522","tid":816444,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:29:01.000Z","msg":"澳門狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b7c68b4fcd34b1b9f9f5eb55b4f254f701a16f","tid":816444,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T18:32:13.000Z","msg":"話真係澳門狗嚟"},{"pid":"0b9745cc8b62ed997d6a1bb3